         <abstract id="aspace_f8d9d602ffd526a0bb11c4d384d6f677">The records consist of maps, studies, news clippings, research notes, presentation panels, and assorted data compiled by Waltraude (Val) Woods, senior architect/planner at Yale Office of Facilities, documenting the history of campus planning and buildings and grounds at Yale University.</abstract>
